              </div>
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-cyan-100 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-cyan-900 transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-cyan-900 group-hover:text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10c0 3.866-3.582 7-8 7a8.841 8.841 0 01-4.083-.98L2 17l1.338-3.123C2.493 12.767 2 11.434 2 10c0-3.866 3.582-7 8-7s8 3.134 8 7zM7 9H5v2h2V9zm8 0h-2v2h2V9zM9 9h2v2H9V9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Creator of functional digital experiences with over 10 years in graphic design and social media strategy.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-900 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Social Media</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-900 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Content</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-900 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Design</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 w-16 h-16 bg-cyan-900 rounded-full opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity blur-2xl"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Team Member 3: Maria Casco -->
      <div class="group relative">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-white shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="relative h-80 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-orange-50">
            <img
              src="/photos/team-code/Mariacasco.png"
              alt="Maria Casco"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-cyan-900 via-cyan-900/50 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>

            <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-0 right-0 flex justify-center gap-3 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-500">
              <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-orange-400 hover:scale-110 transition-all">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-cyan-900" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"/>
                </svg>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="p-6">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-black text-cyan-900 group-hover:text-orange-400 transition-colors">Maria Casco</h3>
                <p class="text-sm font-bold text-orange-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Product Manager</p>
              </div>
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-orange-100 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-orange-400 transition-colors">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-orange-400 group-hover:text-white" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path d="M3 1a1 1 0 000 2h1.22l.305 1.222a.997.997 0 00.01.042l1.358 5.43-.893.892C3.74 11.846 4.632 14 6.414 14H15a1 1 0 000-2H6.414l1-1H14a1 1 0 00.894-.553l3-6A1 1 0 0017 3H6.28l-.31-1.243A1 1 0 005 1H3zM16 16.5a1.5 1.5 0 11-3 0 1.5 1.5 0 013 0zM6.5 18a1.5 1.5 0 100-3 1.5 1.5 0 000 3z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
            </div>

            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Over 10 years in textile and promotional products. Expert in product management and brand-focused merchandise.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-900 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Products</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-900 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Branding</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-900 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Quality</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 w-16 h-16 bg-orange-400 rounded-full opacity-10 group-hover:opacity-20 transition-opacity blur-2xl"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Team Member 4: Larisa Lopez -->
      <div class="group relative">
        <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-white shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="relative h-80 overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-orange-50 to-cyan-50">
            <img
              src="/photos/team-code/Cmorel.png"
              alt="Larisa Lopez"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-cyan-900 via-cyan-900/50 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-500"></div>

            <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-0 right-0 flex justify-center gap-3 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 translate-y-4 group-hover:translate-y-0 transition-all duration-500">
              <a href="#" class="w-10 h-10 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-orange-400 hover:scale-110 transition-all">
