            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
              Over 8 years creating functional and attractive digital experiences. Focus on research and user-centered design.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-900 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">UX/UI</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-900 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Research</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-900 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold">Figma</span>
